      *  LUC116 - Facility Expiry and Last Availability Dates -       *                       
      *             Until Further Notice                              *                       
      *                                                               *                       
      *****************************************************************                       
      *                                                                                       
      ** If LUC116 is enabled, and Day No is 36083 (15OCT70). For                             
      ** Expiry Date (I=2) and/or Last Availability Date (I=11)                               
      ** Display UFN.                                                                         
     C           LUC116    IFEQ 'Y'                                                           
     C           I         ANDEQ2                                                             
     C           DAY,I     ANDEQ36083                                                         
     C           LUC116    OREQ 'Y'                                                           
     C           I         ANDEQ11                                                            
     C           DAY,I     ANDEQ36083                                                         
     C                     MOVE 'UFN    ' DAT,I                                               
     C                     ELSE                                                               
      *****************************************************************                       
      ** End of hook LUC116_003                                                               
      *****************************************************************                       
